{
  "stem": "26111.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sigmund, ?] who was the third, was really a very-- a very physically weak boy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, and he-- so weak that, that he wasn't even good sport for them to, to, to fight with and to beat up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for that we-- Blum and myself-- we sort of stood shoulder to shoulder.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And we had to explain to our parents why we were bloodied when we got home-- very often, not every day, but quite often.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You say it didn't happen every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But was it quite often, as you say, that these incidents--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fairly often, yes--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was something to be-- not to look forward to, shall we say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And, of course, the worst part is you can say these are children, mostly members of Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Many of them were in their Hitler Youth uniforms, came to school that way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- you might say they're still children, nonetheless.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- maybe the worst part about this was the behavior of the masters, the teachers, who had the supervision during the breaks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, it was during the breaks that this happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they just turned their backs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They just turned their backs, engaged in very animated conversation, one with the other, anything, so that they wouldn't have to look that way, where we were getting ours and giving some back, I must say.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only one, and that was very ironic, quite, quite ironic because it was-- I was running.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was not running from anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was simply running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was actually, for a change, playing a running game, I suppose, with somebody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I stumbled, and I fell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I fell with such force that it knocked the breath out of me completely.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
